          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.To control and eliminate the neighborhood",
                "of associated with O-16 levels (6.917 and 7.117 MeV),",
                "produced via the reaction C-12(Li-7,t)O-16, the (Li7,t)",
                "reaction was measured on both C-13 and C-12 targets.",
                "A very small contribution of N-15 levels was also seen."
              ]
            }
